00:01:07.110 --> 00:01:09.360 align:middle line:84%
>> Every one of
you in this room,

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:11.460 align:middle line:84%
you come here this weekend
to the Whole Life Expo,

00:01:11.460 --> 00:01:15.300 align:middle line:84%
because there's a part of
you that wants to learn more

00:01:15.300 --> 00:01:18.240 align:middle line:84%
and want to gain more wisdom,
and there's another part of you

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:19.270 align:middle line:90%
that wants to heal.

00:01:19.270 --> 00:01:22.258 align:middle line:10%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:01:22.258 --> 00:01:26.740 align:middle line:90%


00:01:26.740 --> 00:01:30.210 align:middle line:10%
I talk in my book
about the difference

00:01:30.210 --> 00:01:36.070 align:middle line:10%
between our soul's perspective
and our physical perspective.

00:01:36.070 --> 00:01:40.470 align:middle line:10%
We do have-- we, us
conscious, our conscious minds

00:01:40.470 --> 00:01:41.410 align:middle line:10%
our bodies--

00:01:41.410 --> 00:01:43.500 align:middle line:10%
we do have a different
attitude about things

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:45.840 align:middle line:10%
that our soul does.

00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:49.440 align:middle line:84%
Our soul sees things from a
higher perspective, all right?

00:01:49.440 --> 00:01:52.890 align:middle line:84%
Our soul can actually
look at an experience

00:01:52.890 --> 00:01:56.670 align:middle line:84%
and say, OK, I need
to go through this,

00:01:56.670 --> 00:01:58.920 align:middle line:84%
and I'm going to give you
an example of something that

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:00.090 align:middle line:90%
happened in my life.

00:02:00.090 --> 00:02:03.360 align:middle line:84%
But our soul can kind of step
back and be more objective

00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:05.460 align:middle line:84%
and look at an experience,
and say, OK, I'm

00:02:05.460 --> 00:02:09.270 align:middle line:84%
going through this,
because of this.

00:02:09.270 --> 00:02:11.730 align:middle line:84%
But in the body,
our conscious minds,

00:02:11.730 --> 00:02:14.760 align:middle line:84%
we have a tough time with that,
because we're so emotionally

00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:16.510 align:middle line:90%
involved in our lives.

00:02:16.510 --> 00:02:20.280 align:middle line:84%
And so when we're going
through a tough experience,

00:02:20.280 --> 00:02:22.650 align:middle line:84%
it's hard for us
to detach ourselves

00:02:22.650 --> 00:02:25.050 align:middle line:84%
and look at it from
the highest perspective

00:02:25.050 --> 00:02:28.720 align:middle line:84%
and say, what is the
wisdom in this experience?

00:02:28.720 --> 00:02:31.500 align:middle line:84%
And so that's why
a lot of times, we

00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:37.290 align:middle line:84%
don't know what our
soul's plan is, OK?

00:02:37.290 --> 00:02:40.080 align:middle line:84%
Because it would be hard
for us to understand it.

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:42.860 align:middle line:90%


00:02:42.860 --> 00:02:45.220 align:middle line:84%
And I know that that can
be confusing for people.

00:02:45.220 --> 00:02:47.740 align:middle line:84%
People want it a little
more clear than that.

00:02:47.740 --> 00:02:49.315 align:middle line:90%
But I'll give you an example.

00:02:49.315 --> 00:02:53.720 align:middle line:90%


00:02:53.720 --> 00:02:56.390 align:middle line:84%
When I was young,
I was 19 years old,

00:02:56.390 --> 00:03:01.600 align:middle line:84%
I was a sophomore in college,
I was engaged to a man.

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:04.630 align:middle line:84%
We had a pretty
dysfunctional relationship,

00:03:04.630 --> 00:03:10.300 align:middle line:84%
but I was raised in
an alcoholic family.

00:03:10.300 --> 00:03:16.180 align:middle line:84%
And growing up, I had a
lot of dysfunction in me.

00:03:16.180 --> 00:03:17.470 align:middle line:90%
I had a lot of--

00:03:17.470 --> 00:03:22.090 align:middle line:84%
I had a lot of everything,
a lot of shame about things,

00:03:22.090 --> 00:03:25.720 align:middle line:84%
a lot of rage, a
lot of confusion,

00:03:25.720 --> 00:03:28.000 align:middle line:90%
very, very low self-worth.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:33.654 align:middle line:84%
And I attracted to me
people that kind of--

00:03:33.654 --> 00:03:40.480 align:middle line:84%
honestly, kind of supported the
way that I felt about myself.

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:44.890 align:middle line:84%
But, you know, he looked
great on the outside.

00:03:44.890 --> 00:03:49.195 align:middle line:90%
And I thought, OK, I'll just--

00:03:49.195 --> 00:03:52.150 align:middle line:84%
I'll marry this man, and
we'll have lots of kids,

00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:55.270 align:middle line:84%
and I'll be a social worker,
and he'll be a lawyer,

00:03:55.270 --> 00:03:57.530 align:middle line:84%
and we'll live
happily ever after.

00:03:57.530 --> 00:04:00.760 align:middle line:84%
And the whole inside of
me was just like, oh God.

00:04:00.760 --> 00:04:04.870 align:middle line:84%
I knew, but I was pretending
not to know what I knew.

00:04:04.870 --> 00:04:08.290 align:middle line:84%
And so I was in
this relationship,

00:04:08.290 --> 00:04:12.520 align:middle line:84%
and I found out that I was
pregnant, 19 years old, not

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:13.900 align:middle line:90%
married.

00:04:13.900 --> 00:04:20.440 align:middle line:84%
Now, back then, in 1968,
that was not a cool thing

00:04:20.440 --> 00:04:23.650 align:middle line:90%
to be pregnant and unmarried.

00:04:23.650 --> 00:04:27.790 align:middle line:84%
And my attitude at that time,
again, very low self-worth,

00:04:27.790 --> 00:04:30.850 align:middle line:84%
I thought, why is
God doing this to me?

00:04:30.850 --> 00:04:33.160 align:middle line:90%
Why didn't God prevent this?

00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:38.550 align:middle line:84%
If God really loved me, he
wouldn't have made me pregnant.

00:04:38.550 --> 00:04:41.370 align:middle line:90%
[AUDIENCE LAUGHTER]

00:04:41.370 --> 00:04:44.200 align:middle line:90%


00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:47.370 align:middle line:84%
But I was raised a
Presbyterian, OK,

00:04:47.370 --> 00:04:50.290 align:middle line:84%
and I had the belief that if bad
things happened in your life,

00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:52.390 align:middle line:90%
it came from God.

00:04:52.390 --> 00:04:57.910 align:middle line:84%
And so I had to look at
my life, because here was

00:04:57.910 --> 00:05:02.650 align:middle line:90%
this very painful situation.

00:05:02.650 --> 00:05:06.270 align:middle line:84%
And I looked at my
boyfriend and realized--

00:05:06.270 --> 00:05:08.320 align:middle line:84%
it was just like the
whole experience just

00:05:08.320 --> 00:05:10.240 align:middle line:90%
slapped me in the face.

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:12.440 align:middle line:84%
I thought, oh my
God, I can't do this.

00:05:12.440 --> 00:05:13.840 align:middle line:90%
I cannot do this.

00:05:13.840 --> 00:05:17.350 align:middle line:84%
As much as here I'm
engaged to this--

00:05:17.350 --> 00:05:20.770 align:middle line:84%
everybody thought he
was a wonderful guy.

00:05:20.770 --> 00:05:23.080 align:middle line:84%
You know, he had
a lot of promise.

00:05:23.080 --> 00:05:24.330 align:middle line:90%
Straight A's in college.

00:05:24.330 --> 00:05:26.260 align:middle line:84%
He was going to go
on to be an attorney.

00:05:26.260 --> 00:05:28.455 align:middle line:84%
We were going to
have this great life.

00:05:28.455 --> 00:05:30.580 align:middle line:84%
But everything just kind
of slapped me in the face,

00:05:30.580 --> 00:05:32.563 align:middle line:84%
and I went, whoa,
this is-- well,

00:05:32.563 --> 00:05:33.980 align:middle line:84%
I didn't say the
word dysfunction.

00:05:33.980 --> 00:05:37.060 align:middle line:84%
Back then, I didn't hear the
word dysfunction back then.

00:05:37.060 --> 00:05:38.560 align:middle line:90%
But you just knew.

00:05:38.560 --> 00:05:41.890 align:middle line:84%
I knew inside,
this is not right.

00:05:41.890 --> 00:05:47.710 align:middle line:84%
And so I had been raised
by a mother who had taught

00:05:47.710 --> 00:05:50.110 align:middle line:90%
me to listen to my inner voice.

00:05:50.110 --> 00:05:53.140 align:middle line:84%
And I went to my inner
voice and said what do I do?

00:05:53.140 --> 00:05:57.070 align:middle line:84%
And my inner voice said,
you have this baby,

00:05:57.070 --> 00:05:59.320 align:middle line:90%
and you place him for adoption.

00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:01.420 align:middle line:84%
And I said to my
boyfriend, this is

00:06:01.420 --> 00:06:05.500 align:middle line:84%
what I have to do as
painful as it was.

00:06:05.500 --> 00:06:10.690 align:middle line:84%
Again, throughout my pregnancy,
I felt really, really bad.

00:06:10.690 --> 00:06:13.270 align:middle line:90%
I felt like about this high.

00:06:13.270 --> 00:06:15.070 align:middle line:84%
How could I do
this to my family?

00:06:15.070 --> 00:06:18.580 align:middle line:84%
I felt awful about
doing this to my child,

00:06:18.580 --> 00:06:20.350 align:middle line:84%
because my father
had been adopted,

00:06:20.350 --> 00:06:24.530 align:middle line:84%
and he had been adopted into a
very, very dysfunctional family

00:06:24.530 --> 00:06:25.330 align:middle line:90%
system.

00:06:25.330 --> 00:06:28.840 align:middle line:84%
A lot of bad, bad stuff
had happened to my dad.

00:06:28.840 --> 00:06:30.340 align:middle line:84%
And so all throughout
the pregnancy,

00:06:30.340 --> 00:06:34.030 align:middle line:84%
I had this fear that this was
going to happen to my son.

00:06:34.030 --> 00:06:40.990 align:middle line:10%
And so it was a very hard time,
and yet, I mean, I look back,

00:06:40.990 --> 00:06:45.160 align:middle line:10%
and I think, so
much pain went on

00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:47.740 align:middle line:10%
because of my low
self-worth, because

00:06:47.740 --> 00:06:50.860 align:middle line:10%
of how I was looking
at the experience.

00:06:50.860 --> 00:06:55.000 align:middle line:10%
I placed my son for
adoption, and it

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:58.720 align:middle line:10%
continued for a long,
long, long, long time

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:02.440 align:middle line:10%
to be a very painful
experience inside.

00:07:02.440 --> 00:07:08.690 align:middle line:84%
And I went from thinking, why
did God do that to me to kind

00:07:08.690 --> 00:07:11.250 align:middle line:84%
of the new age way of
thinking-- this was back

00:07:11.250 --> 00:07:12.640 align:middle line:90%
in the '60s and '70s--

00:07:12.640 --> 00:07:15.630 align:middle line:84%
of I must have done
something terrible

00:07:15.630 --> 00:07:19.830 align:middle line:84%
to another woman in a past life
to have to give up my child.

00:07:19.830 --> 00:07:22.260 align:middle line:84%
I must have taken a child
away from another woman

00:07:22.260 --> 00:07:23.640 align:middle line:90%
or something.

00:07:23.640 --> 00:07:28.590 align:middle line:84%
And I must have been
really, really bad person

00:07:28.590 --> 00:07:31.950 align:middle line:84%
to have had to go
through that experience.

00:07:31.950 --> 00:07:36.990 align:middle line:84%
As I continued to heal
myself, my perspective

00:07:36.990 --> 00:07:41.620 align:middle line:84%
of that whole
experience changed.

00:07:41.620 --> 00:07:46.260 align:middle line:10%
And that's a lot
of what we're doing

00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:50.040 align:middle line:10%
is as we heal
ourselves, as we go

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:51.780 align:middle line:10%
through these
painful experiences,

00:07:51.780 --> 00:07:56.130 align:middle line:10%
and we heal ourselves,
our perspective changes.

00:07:56.130 --> 00:07:59.620 align:middle line:10%
And the more that
we heal ourselves,

00:07:59.620 --> 00:08:03.000 align:middle line:10%
then we start to see the
wisdom in the experience.

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:06.570 align:middle line:84%
It's no longer, why
did God do this to me?

00:08:06.570 --> 00:08:11.350 align:middle line:84%
It's no longer this happened
to me because I'm a bad person.

00:08:11.350 --> 00:08:13.530 align:middle line:84%
It's no longer
this happened to me

00:08:13.530 --> 00:08:16.320 align:middle line:84%
because I was a terrible
person in a past life.

00:08:16.320 --> 00:08:20.350 align:middle line:90%


00:08:20.350 --> 00:08:26.530 align:middle line:84%
Seven years ago, my
inner voice told me

00:08:26.530 --> 00:08:28.980 align:middle line:84%
that I could start
to look for my son.

00:08:28.980 --> 00:08:32.650 align:middle line:84%
Now, I had asked God ever
since my son turned 18,

00:08:32.650 --> 00:08:35.080 align:middle line:84%
I had asked him, can I
start looking for him?

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:40.770 align:middle line:84%
And every time I meditated on
it, I'd hear not yet, not yet.

00:08:40.770 --> 00:08:42.539 align:middle line:10%
And I kept working
on myself, and I

00:08:42.539 --> 00:08:44.550 align:middle line:10%
kept working on this path.

00:08:44.550 --> 00:08:47.080 align:middle line:90%
And I got to a place--

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:49.400 align:middle line:90%
I think it was 1992--

00:08:49.400 --> 00:08:52.470 align:middle line:84%
where some major healing
had taken place inside of me

00:08:52.470 --> 00:08:56.580 align:middle line:84%
and some big chunks of
self-worth had healed.

00:08:56.580 --> 00:08:58.950 align:middle line:84%
And one morning, I woke
up, and a voice said,

00:08:58.950 --> 00:09:00.655 align:middle line:90%
you can look for your son now.

00:09:00.655 --> 00:09:02.280 align:middle line:84%
You can start to look
for your son now.

00:09:02.280 --> 00:09:06.210 align:middle line:84%
And all of the pieces
fell into place for me.

00:09:06.210 --> 00:09:08.180 align:middle line:90%
And I met my son.

00:09:08.180 --> 00:09:14.100 align:middle line:84%
And we have developed, like, a
totally cool, totally wonderful

00:09:14.100 --> 00:09:17.320 align:middle line:90%
mother-son relationship.

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:21.700 align:middle line:84%
And now, my perspective
is completely different.

00:09:21.700 --> 00:09:23.850 align:middle line:10%
It's no longer--
none of that happened

00:09:23.850 --> 00:09:28.290 align:middle line:10%
because I was a bad person or
because God was punishing me

00:09:28.290 --> 00:09:33.090 align:middle line:10%
for having premarital
sex or because I was

00:09:33.090 --> 00:09:35.730 align:middle line:10%
a bad person in a past life.

00:09:35.730 --> 00:09:38.490 align:middle line:90%
It happened because it happened.

00:09:38.490 --> 00:09:44.010 align:middle line:84%
It happened because I gained
so much from the experience.

00:09:44.010 --> 00:09:46.920 align:middle line:84%
I came into this lifetime
to do the work that I'm

00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:51.210 align:middle line:84%
talking to you about today to
get to develop my abilities,

00:09:51.210 --> 00:09:52.890 align:middle line:90%
to do the work that I've done.

00:09:52.890 --> 00:09:58.080 align:middle line:84%
My work-- I never had any
other children after that.

00:09:58.080 --> 00:10:01.680 align:middle line:84%
My work has been my
life, and I really

00:10:01.680 --> 00:10:05.580 align:middle line:84%
believe that that's what's
been important to my soul is

00:10:05.580 --> 00:10:08.070 align:middle line:84%
to come in and do the
work that I've done,

00:10:08.070 --> 00:10:11.813 align:middle line:84%
develop my abilities,
heal myself.

00:10:11.813 --> 00:10:13.230 align:middle line:84%
And believe me,
I'm not there yet.

00:10:13.230 --> 00:10:14.800 align:middle line:90%
Still got a ways to go.

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:17.790 align:middle line:84%
This whole self-worth thing, boy
I tell you, it's a tough one.

00:10:17.790 --> 00:10:22.590 align:middle line:90%


00:10:22.590 --> 00:10:26.590 align:middle line:84%
I came in to do the
work that I'm doing.

00:10:26.590 --> 00:10:29.860 align:middle line:84%
But my soul also
wanted to be a mother.

00:10:29.860 --> 00:10:35.530 align:middle line:84%
And my son grew up in a
wonderful family who loves him.

00:10:35.530 --> 00:10:37.340 align:middle line:90%
They're very grateful for him.

00:10:37.340 --> 00:10:40.520 align:middle line:84%
He turned out to be a totally
wonderful human being.

00:10:40.520 --> 00:10:42.940 align:middle line:84%
And I think back on what
it would have been like

00:10:42.940 --> 00:10:45.220 align:middle line:84%
if I would have raised
him, and I don't think

00:10:45.220 --> 00:10:46.425 align:middle line:90%
it would have been so good.

00:10:46.425 --> 00:10:48.050 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, I love him,
but I would have been

00:10:48.050 --> 00:10:49.480 align:middle line:90%
an extremely overprotective.

00:10:49.480 --> 00:10:51.813 align:middle line:84%
I've told him many times, I
would have put you in a room

00:10:51.813 --> 00:10:54.820 align:middle line:84%
and kept you in there until you
were 20 and let you out maybe.

00:10:54.820 --> 00:10:55.720 align:middle line:90%
I was so--

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:59.260 align:middle line:84%
I didn't I wouldn't have
wanted anything in life

00:10:59.260 --> 00:11:03.360 align:middle line:84%
to touch him or hurt him
or give him any pain.

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:06.040 align:middle line:90%
I would have been obsessive.

00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:09.380 align:middle line:84%
I had so much dysfunction
in me that had to heal.

00:11:09.380 --> 00:11:13.440 align:middle line:84%
And so I see the
reason for that now.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:15.660 align:middle line:84%
I didn't see it while
I was in the pain,

00:11:15.660 --> 00:11:19.170 align:middle line:84%
but as I've healed from
the pain, I can look back,

00:11:19.170 --> 00:11:21.090 align:middle line:90%
and I can see it now.

00:11:21.090 --> 00:11:25.350 align:middle line:84%
So that's what I mean when
I say that as we heal,

00:11:25.350 --> 00:11:28.680 align:middle line:84%
our perspective
changes, and we start

00:11:28.680 --> 00:11:32.730 align:middle line:84%
to see these experiences that
we've come in here to have.

00:11:32.730 --> 00:11:35.770 align:middle line:10%
We see them differently.

00:11:35.770 --> 00:11:39.640 align:middle line:84%
We don't see them through
the eyes of low self-worth.

00:11:39.640 --> 00:11:42.480 align:middle line:84%
We don't go through the
pain, thinking I deserve this

00:11:42.480 --> 00:11:44.370 align:middle line:90%
because I'm a bad person.

00:11:44.370 --> 00:11:47.660 align:middle line:84%
Every one of you in this
room, you come here this week

00:11:47.660 --> 00:11:49.770 align:middle line:84%
into the Whole Life
Expo, because there's

00:11:49.770 --> 00:11:52.530 align:middle line:84%
a part of you that
wants to learn more,

00:11:52.530 --> 00:11:54.330 align:middle line:90%
you want to gain more wisdom.

00:11:54.330 --> 00:11:57.270 align:middle line:84%
And there's another part
