00:14:18.580 --> 00:14:23.420 align:middle line:84%
and finally got into
recovery and got on my path.

00:14:23.420 --> 00:14:25.180 align:middle line:84%
But that was the
thing I was avoiding.

00:14:25.180 --> 00:14:27.305 align:middle line:84%
You know, it was like every
time, I'd take a drink,

00:14:27.305 --> 00:14:29.650 align:middle line:90%
I'd think I know--

00:14:29.650 --> 00:14:31.990 align:middle line:84%
it's like, I don't
know how they knew,

00:14:31.990 --> 00:14:33.490 align:middle line:84%
but every time I'd
head for the bar,

00:14:33.490 --> 00:14:34.780 align:middle line:90%
they'd head down there, too.

00:14:34.780 --> 00:14:37.740 align:middle line:90%
[AUDIENCE LAUGHTER]

00:14:37.740 --> 00:14:41.340 align:middle line:84%
And I'd go to take that drink,
and there they'd be, you know?

00:14:41.340 --> 00:14:44.190 align:middle line:90%
You're like, oh God.

00:14:44.190 --> 00:14:46.700 align:middle line:84%
And so there was
always this struggle.

00:14:46.700 --> 00:14:49.200 align:middle line:84%
And I always thought it was
them that I was struggling with.

00:14:49.200 --> 00:14:51.360 align:middle line:90%
But it was inside of me.

00:14:51.360 --> 00:14:53.850 align:middle line:84%
I knew-- you know, I could
look back now and see

00:14:53.850 --> 00:14:56.910 align:middle line:84%
that I chose to come
into an alcoholic family

00:14:56.910 --> 00:14:58.770 align:middle line:84%
because I had been
alcoholic before,

00:14:58.770 --> 00:15:00.240 align:middle line:90%
and I had never dealt with it.

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:01.980 align:middle line:90%
I just kept dying a drunk.

00:15:01.980 --> 00:15:05.410 align:middle line:84%
It was time to come in and deal
with it and get on your path.

00:15:05.410 --> 00:15:07.520 align:middle line:90%
And that's what I came in to do.

00:15:07.520 --> 00:15:09.930 align:middle line:84%
And so I chose the
perfect family system

00:15:09.930 --> 00:15:14.310 align:middle line:84%
to do that in, except
growing up in it,

00:15:14.310 --> 00:15:16.680 align:middle line:84%
again, I thought, why
is God doing this to me?

00:15:16.680 --> 00:15:19.020 align:middle line:84%
You know, they say Jesus
loves you, God loves you.

00:15:19.020 --> 00:15:21.410 align:middle line:90%
Well, hey, what about me?

00:15:21.410 --> 00:15:26.220 align:middle line:84%
OK, so I always saw it
as God didn't love me.

00:15:26.220 --> 00:15:28.410 align:middle line:90%
God wasn't protecting me.

00:15:28.410 --> 00:15:29.850 align:middle line:90%
And why me?

00:15:29.850 --> 00:15:33.000 align:middle line:84%
So for a long time, my life
was about why me, why me,

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:36.160 align:middle line:84%
why me until things
started to change.

00:15:36.160 --> 00:15:41.640 align:middle line:84%
And again, as we heal,
our perspective changes.

00:15:41.640 --> 00:15:45.600 align:middle line:84%
And then we start to see all the
really cool stuff about life.

00:15:45.600 --> 00:15:49.310 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I love-- today, I love
the family that I grew up in.

00:15:49.310 --> 00:15:53.680 align:middle line:84%
But I couldn't have said
that for a long time.

00:15:53.680 --> 00:15:55.550 align:middle line:84%
I used to think poor
me all the time.

00:15:55.550 --> 00:15:57.040 align:middle line:84%
Grew up with two
alcoholic parents.

00:15:57.040 --> 00:15:57.840 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:15:57.840 --> 00:15:59.310 align:middle line:90%
Why me?

00:15:59.310 --> 00:16:00.810 align:middle line:90%
I was a very sad person.

00:16:00.810 --> 00:16:03.300 align:middle line:90%
I was a very rageful person.

00:16:03.300 --> 00:16:06.520 align:middle line:84%
And so there was a
lot of pain to heal,

00:16:06.520 --> 00:16:10.770 align:middle line:84%
but I know now that when I
was born into that family,

00:16:10.770 --> 00:16:13.200 align:middle line:84%
I already had that
rage inside me.

00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:16.230 align:middle line:84%
I already had that pain
there, and my family just

00:16:16.230 --> 00:16:19.540 align:middle line:84%
helped to bring it up
to the surface, you see?

00:16:19.540 --> 00:16:22.290 align:middle line:84%
So if you could look
into your family systems,

00:16:22.290 --> 00:16:26.430 align:middle line:84%
look into your life, look at
the painful situations that

00:16:26.430 --> 00:16:30.540 align:middle line:84%
are going on in your life,
and just say, OK, now,

00:16:30.540 --> 00:16:32.040 align:middle line:90%
what is the wisdom in this?

00:16:32.040 --> 00:16:35.820 align:middle line:84%
Why would the elders
or why would I

00:16:35.820 --> 00:16:40.630 align:middle line:84%
have chosen to have this
situation go on in my life?

00:16:40.630 --> 00:16:44.790 align:middle line:84%
And then, after we'd
been here, and we've

00:16:44.790 --> 00:16:50.760 align:middle line:84%
healed as much as we can,
as much as our souls can,

00:16:50.760 --> 00:16:56.965 align:middle line:84%
we lay the body down, and we
go back home, and we rest.

00:16:56.965 --> 00:16:57.765 align:middle line:90%
We take a break.

00:16:57.765 --> 00:16:58.830 align:middle line:10%
We take a long break.

00:16:58.830 --> 00:17:00.600 align:middle line:90%
We take a short break.

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:05.040 align:middle line:84%
They say usually between 60 and
100 years between lifetimes.

00:17:05.040 --> 00:17:07.920 align:middle line:84%
Some people come back
quicker, but that's not

00:17:07.920 --> 00:17:10.920 align:middle line:84%
advised, because it can
be kind of confusing.

00:17:10.920 --> 00:17:14.579 align:middle line:84%
Still have the identity
of the last person.

00:17:14.579 --> 00:17:16.020 align:middle line:90%
So we come in.

00:17:16.020 --> 00:17:19.560 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we go back, and
we stay on the other side.

00:17:19.560 --> 00:17:21.630 align:middle line:84%
And after we're
home for a while,

00:17:21.630 --> 00:17:23.760 align:middle line:84%
our heads have kind
of cleared out.

00:17:23.760 --> 00:17:25.530 align:middle line:90%
Then we do a life review.

00:17:25.530 --> 00:17:27.540 align:middle line:84%
And the life review
takes place over

00:17:27.540 --> 00:17:29.520 align:middle line:84%
a long, long, long,
long period of time.

00:17:29.520 --> 00:17:32.460 align:middle line:84%
It isn't like something
you go and do in a week.

00:17:32.460 --> 00:17:35.760 align:middle line:84%
Again, it has to do with
your perspective, how

00:17:35.760 --> 00:17:38.370 align:middle line:90%
you see things.

00:17:38.370 --> 00:17:42.090 align:middle line:10%
And you record it all in your
case your Akashic records,

00:17:42.090 --> 00:17:44.910 align:middle line:10%
and then you just take a
break, and you hang out

00:17:44.910 --> 00:17:48.750 align:middle line:10%
with all those other souls
that on the other side,

00:17:48.750 --> 00:17:51.842 align:middle line:10%
because when we
go home, we see--

00:17:51.842 --> 00:17:52.800 align:middle line:10%
I mean, think about it.

00:17:52.800 --> 00:17:54.175 align:middle line:10%
Just think about
it for a second.

00:17:54.175 --> 00:17:57.810 align:middle line:84%
Let's say all of us in this
room have had 300 lifetimes, OK?

00:17:57.810 --> 00:18:00.420 align:middle line:84%
Buddha said that
it took 550 lives

00:18:00.420 --> 00:18:02.910 align:middle line:90%
before he became the Buddha.

00:18:02.910 --> 00:18:05.470 align:middle line:84%
OK, so let's just say that
all of us have had 300 lives.

00:18:05.470 --> 00:18:07.320 align:middle line:84%
Think of all the
souls that you know.

00:18:07.320 --> 00:18:08.910 align:middle line:90%
It's so cool.

00:18:08.910 --> 00:18:11.760 align:middle line:84%
So when we go home,
it's like a big reunion.

00:18:11.760 --> 00:18:13.800 align:middle line:84%
You know, hey, I'm
back from school.

00:18:13.800 --> 00:18:15.870 align:middle line:84%
Man, you should hear
the things I learned.

00:18:15.870 --> 00:18:17.070 align:middle line:90%
Oh, yeah?

00:18:17.070 --> 00:18:19.410 align:middle line:90%
And we share it with them.

00:18:19.410 --> 00:18:21.450 align:middle line:90%
And we run into old friends.

00:18:21.450 --> 00:18:26.640 align:middle line:84%
And it's just like the
coolest thing to go back home.

00:18:26.640 --> 00:18:29.230 align:middle line:84%
Death is, unfortunately,
portrayed to us-- well,

00:18:29.230 --> 00:18:31.710 align:middle line:84%
of course, to us, it's
our physical body.

00:18:31.710 --> 00:18:35.880 align:middle line:84%
You know, we don't
want to think about it.

00:18:35.880 --> 00:18:38.280 align:middle line:84%
Like the guide said, when
God created our bodies,

00:18:38.280 --> 00:18:42.670 align:middle line:84%
he created our bodies with a
very strong desire to survive.

00:18:42.670 --> 00:18:44.900 align:middle line:84%
So we don't want to
hear about death.

00:18:44.900 --> 00:18:48.050 align:middle line:84%
But I can tell you,
I can guarantee you

00:18:48.050 --> 00:18:51.830 align:middle line:84%
that when it is time for you
to lay down that body and go,

00:18:51.830 --> 00:18:54.500 align:middle line:84%
death is probably going to be
the easiest thing you will ever

00:18:54.500 --> 00:18:56.510 align:middle line:90%
do, because it's simply--

00:18:56.510 --> 00:18:59.330 align:middle line:90%
it's like taking off a sweater.

00:18:59.330 --> 00:19:02.480 align:middle line:84%
You just step out of your
body, and you go on home,

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:04.085 align:middle line:84%
and you see all
kinds of friends.

00:19:04.085 --> 00:19:05.960 align:middle line:10%
Do you want to here a
cool little baby story?

00:19:05.960 --> 00:19:07.543 align:middle line:10%
I just learned this
one the other day.

00:19:07.543 --> 00:19:10.630 align:middle line:10%
So I want to tell
everybody the story.

00:19:10.630 --> 00:19:12.650 align:middle line:10%
I have a girlfriend
who's pregnant.

00:19:12.650 --> 00:19:15.680 align:middle line:84%
Well, she just had her baby,
but girlfriend who's pregnant,

00:19:15.680 --> 00:19:21.830 align:middle line:84%
and about a month ago, I
wanted to make the baby

00:19:21.830 --> 00:19:26.732 align:middle line:84%
a blanket, and so I wasn't
sure about the timing.

00:19:26.732 --> 00:19:28.940 align:middle line:84%
Everybody said-- she had
like three different doctors

00:19:28.940 --> 00:19:30.190 align:middle line:90%
and three different due dates.

00:19:30.190 --> 00:19:35.670 align:middle line:84%
And so I just said I'd like to
talk to the soul of the baby.

00:19:35.670 --> 00:19:39.390 align:middle line:84%
And so that soul
came into my house.

00:19:39.390 --> 00:19:41.300 align:middle line:90%
She just came in, totally cool.

00:19:41.300 --> 00:19:44.010 align:middle line:84%
And I said, when are
you going to be born?

00:19:44.010 --> 00:19:45.510 align:middle line:84%
I said, I want to
make this blanket,

00:19:45.510 --> 00:19:48.170 align:middle line:84%
and I just need to know
if I have enough time.

00:19:48.170 --> 00:19:52.500 align:middle line:90%
And she said, oh, don't worry.

00:19:52.500 --> 00:19:56.570 align:middle line:84%
I have to be on the other
side until at least August 30.

00:19:56.570 --> 00:20:00.610 align:middle line:90%
I have to be there August 30.

00:20:00.610 --> 00:20:01.520 align:middle line:90%
I have to be there.

00:20:01.520 --> 00:20:02.395 align:middle line:90%
I said, OK.

00:20:02.395 --> 00:20:05.020 align:middle line:84%
All right, so you're not coming
until after the 30th of August.

00:20:05.020 --> 00:20:06.160 align:middle line:90%
That's right.

00:20:06.160 --> 00:20:07.900 align:middle line:84%
She says, then after
that, you know,

00:20:07.900 --> 00:20:09.192 align:middle line:90%
I can come any time after that.

00:20:09.192 --> 00:20:10.610 align:middle line:90%
I have-- OK.

00:20:10.610 --> 00:20:11.410 align:middle line:90%
All right, thanks.

00:20:11.410 --> 00:20:12.410 align:middle line:90%
Gives me plenty of time.

00:20:12.410 --> 00:20:13.250 align:middle line:90%
All right.

00:20:13.250 --> 00:20:18.360 align:middle line:84%
So I got the blanket done,
and August 30, my friend

00:20:18.360 --> 00:20:19.857 align:middle line:90%
started having contractions.

00:20:19.857 --> 00:20:22.190 align:middle line:84%
And I was over channeling the
healing to her because she

00:20:22.190 --> 00:20:24.140 align:middle line:90%
had a sinus infection.

00:20:24.140 --> 00:20:25.430 align:middle line:90%
And it was really cool.

00:20:25.430 --> 00:20:27.560 align:middle line:84%
Into the room-- oh, I
had asked her that day.

00:20:27.560 --> 00:20:29.060 align:middle line:84%
What's the big deal
about August 30?

00:20:29.060 --> 00:20:31.352 align:middle line:84%
She just looked at me like,
it's none of your business.

00:20:31.352 --> 00:20:33.410 align:middle line:90%
OK, sorry.

00:20:33.410 --> 00:20:34.220 align:middle line:90%
And she had left.

00:20:34.220 --> 00:20:36.950 align:middle line:84%
OK, so that on August 30, I'm
channeling a healing to her,

00:20:36.950 --> 00:20:39.980 align:middle line:84%
and a beautiful angel came
into the room, and said,

00:20:39.980 --> 00:20:42.530 align:middle line:84%
hello, my name is
Gloria, and I'm

00:20:42.530 --> 00:20:45.180 align:middle line:84%
going to be your
daughter's guardian angel.

00:20:45.180 --> 00:20:46.550 align:middle line:90%
That's totally cool.

00:20:46.550 --> 00:20:48.440 align:middle line:90%
So I told my friend that.

00:20:48.440 --> 00:20:49.670 align:middle line:90%
And I said--

00:20:49.670 --> 00:20:52.850 align:middle line:90%


00:20:52.850 --> 00:20:54.560 align:middle line:90%
I said, where is--

00:20:54.560 --> 00:20:55.860 align:middle line:90%
where is the soul?

00:20:55.860 --> 00:20:58.340 align:middle line:84%
I mean, today's August
30, and I know something

00:20:58.340 --> 00:20:59.780 align:middle line:90%
was real important for her.

00:20:59.780 --> 00:21:04.250 align:middle line:84%
And the angel said to
me, today, a friend

00:21:04.250 --> 00:21:09.140 align:middle line:84%
of hers who is living
in Pakistan is dying,

00:21:09.140 --> 00:21:12.470 align:middle line:84%
and she's going to be coming
over to the other side,

00:21:12.470 --> 00:21:16.550 align:middle line:84%
and this soul is the first
soul that this woman is going

00:21:16.550 --> 00:21:20.960 align:middle line:84%
to look for, because she
was her granddaughter

00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:24.335 align:middle line:84%
in this last life, and
she died when she was six.

00:21:24.335 --> 00:21:27.610 align:middle line:90%


00:21:27.610 --> 00:21:30.760 align:middle line:84%
And she said, she's going
to be there to greet her

00:21:30.760 --> 00:21:34.870 align:middle line:84%
